dcterms:description: The HCP S1200 dataset contains minimally preprocessed resting-state fMRI and task-evoked fMRI data from 1200 subjects, most of whom performed all 23 tasks across 7 categories, including working memory, gambling, motor, language, social cognition, relational processing, and emotion processing tasks.
dcterms:title: HCP S1200
